{"tid":1756270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post求幫推］和理放工","createTime":"2019-11-26T03:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T03:16:33.000Z","uid":227858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1d82657243ba7fde7c3dae565e2d9c44a7ae5e","tid":1756270,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"之前開左好似無咩人知，淨係推d無用post<br />\n再開<br />\n我宣布每日poly和理放工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755704</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動大家未有共識繼唔繼續，但係每日中環和理lunch都好成功同埋係繼續到，所以九龍人每日放工都好似今日咁聲援poly，其實應該唔難做到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家必須記得，今次嘅小勝係幾多人付出左好多先換返來，poly嘅手足依家係食緊發曬霉嘅嘢食，隨時d狗攻入去，一出黎就10年。<br />\n麻煩大家同班泛民議員唔好放棄佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>應承我 每晚放工時間6-7點 poly科學館徑集結 好唔好？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f7eafb9de956ee2a0b766fad65874638e04988b2","tid":1756270,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd93ea7c782fcf6bca509664c039ce1821ed9f1e","tid":1756270,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76a347ec8a6ee2322bc5f5b34cb9206bb7feedda","tid":1756270,"uid":227858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a2ac3ea29e2b46adb11832fa3a056e4f4a5bf83","tid":1756270,"uid":333236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"救手足, 全力支持, 昨晚去了支援, 很被感動,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們需要支援手足, 好手足需要我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s